  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Active play and sports has shown to be effective intervention in managing depression.&#xD;
      Extending the support with Mind body therapy, Revival Active Program was designed as an early&#xD;
      intervention for adolescents.&#xD;
&#xD;
      To measure the efficacy and feasibility of the community based revival active play&#xD;
      intervention for adolescent depression, present pilot study was undertaken.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
